---
layout: base.njk
permalink: /contact.html
title: 無料相談・お問い合わせ
activePage: contact
---

<!-- Page Header -->
<section class="pt-32 pb-16 bg-cream">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-10">
    <p class="section-label mb-6">Contact</p>
    <h1 class="font-serif text-5xl md:text-6xl text-ink">無料相談・<br class="sm:hidden">お問い合わせ</h1>
    <p class="text-muted text-base mt-4 max-w-lg">売りたい・買いたい・活用したい——どんな段階でもお気軽にご相談ください。まずは話を聞くだけでも大丈夫です。</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Consultation Type + Form -->
<section class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-10" x-data="{ consultType: '' }">

    <!-- 相談種別 -->
    <div class="mb-10">
      <p class="text-xs font-medium text-muted mb-4 tracking-widest font-mono-label">STEP 01 — 相談の種類を選んでください</p>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-3">
        <button type="button"
          @click="consultType = 'free'"
          :class="consultType === 'free' ? 'border-[#E8621A] bg-[#E8621A]/5 text-ink' : 'border-[#DDD9D2] text-muted hover:border-ink'"
          class="relative flex flex-col items-start gap-2 p-5 border-2 transition-colors text-left rounded-sm">
          <span class="font-serif text-base text-ink font-medium">無料相談</span>
          <span class="text-xs leading-relaxed">何から始めればいいかわからない。まず話を聞きたい方向け。</span>
          <span x-show="consultType === 'free'" class="absolute top-3 right-3 w-4 h-4 rounded-full bg-[#E8621A] flex items-center justify-center" style="display:none;">
            <svg class="w-2.5 h-2.5 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
          </span>
        </button>
        <button type="button"
          @click="consultType = 'renovation'"
          :class="consultType === 'renovation' ? 'border-[#E8621A] bg-[#E8621A]/5 text-ink' : 'border-[#DDD9D2] text-muted hover:border-ink'"
          class="relative flex flex-col items-start gap-2 p-5 border-2 transition-colors text-left rounded-sm">
          <span class="font-serif text-base text-ink font-medium">リフォーム込み相談</span>
          <span class="text-xs leading-relaxed">中古＋リノベで検討中。物件と工事費を合わせて相談したい。</span>
          <span x-show="consultType === 'renovation'" class="absolute top-3 right-3 w-4 h-4 rounded-full bg-[#E8621A] flex items-center justify-center" style="display:none;">
            <svg class="w-2.5 h-2.5 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
          </span>
        </button>
        <button type="button"
          @click="consultType = 'investment'"
          :class="consultType === 'investment' ? 'border-[#E8621A] bg-[#E8621A]/5 text-ink' : 'border-[#DDD9D2] text-muted hover:border-ink'"
          class="relative flex flex-col items-start gap-2 p-5 border-2 transition-colors text-left rounded-sm">
          <span class="font-serif text-base text-ink font-medium">投資・活用相談</span>
          <span class="text-xs leading-relaxed">収益物件・買取・相続・資産活用について相談したい。</span>
          <span x-show="consultType === 'investment'" class="absolute top-3 right-3 w-4 h-4 rounded-full bg-[#E8621A] flex items-center justify-center" style="display:none;">
            <svg class="w-2.5 h-2.5 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
          </span>
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- フォーム -->
    <p class="text-xs font-medium text-muted mb-6 tracking-widest font-mono-label">STEP 02 — お名前・連絡先を入力してください</p>
    <p class="text-xs text-muted mb-8">フォームからの送信機能は準備中です。送信ボタンを押すと案内が表示されます。お急ぎの場合はお電話でお問い合わせください。</p>
    <form id="contact-form" class="space-y-6" novalidate>
      <input type="hidden" id="consult-type-hidden" name="consult-type" :value="consultType">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-5">
        <div>
          <label class="block text-xs font-medium text-muted mb-2" for="name">お名前 *</label>
          <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-[#DDD9D2] bg-white text-sm text-ink focus:border-ink focus:outline-none transition-colors">
        </div>
        <div>
          <label class="block text-xs font-medium text-muted mb-2" for="furigana">フリガナ *</label>
          <input type="text" id="furigana" name="furigana" required class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-[#DDD9D2] bg-white text-sm text-ink focus:border-ink focus:outline-none transition-colors">
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-5">
        <div>
          <label class="block text-xs font-medium text-muted mb-2" for="email">メールアドレス *</label>
          <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-[#DDD9D2] bg-white text-sm text-ink focus:border-ink focus:outline-none transition-colors">
        </div>
        <div>
          <label class="block text-xs font-medium text-muted mb-2" for="phone">電話番号 *</label>
          <input type="tel" id="phone" name="phone" required class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-[#DDD9D2] bg-white text-sm text-ink focus:border-ink focus:outline-none transition-colors">
        </div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <label class="block text-xs font-medium text-muted mb-2" for="inquiry-type">相談内容の詳細 *</label>
        <select id="inquiry-type" name="inquiry-type" required class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-[#DDD9D2] bg-white text-sm text-ink focus:border-ink focus:outline-none transition-colors">
          <option value="">選択してください</option>
          <option value="無料相談（まず話を聞きたい）">無料相談（まず話を聞きたい）</option>
          <option value="仲介＋リノベ相談">仲介＋リノベ相談</option>
          <option value="買取再販（売りたい）">買取再販（売りたい）</option>
          <option value="収益不動産相談">収益不動産相談</option>
          <option value="相続・空き家相談">相続・空き家相談</option>
          <option value="その他">その他</option>
        </select>
      </div>
      <div>
        <label class="block text-xs font-medium text-muted mb-2" for="message">ご相談内容 *</label>
        <textarea id="message" name="message" required rows="6" class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-[#DDD9D2] bg-white text-sm text-ink focus:border-ink focus:outline-none transition-colors" placeholder="現在の状況やご相談したいことを自由にご記入ください（まだ漠然としていても大丈夫です）"></textarea>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
        <input type="checkbox" id="privacy-agree" name="privacy-agree" required class="mt-1 w-4 h-4 border-[#DDD9D2] accent-[#1A1A1A]">
        <label class="text-xs text-muted" for="privacy-agree"><a href="/privacy.html" class="text-ink hover:text-[#E8621A] transition-colors underline underline-offset-2" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">プライバシーポリシー</a>に同意する</label>
      </div>
      <button type="submit" class="w-full py-4 bg-[#1A1A1A] text-[#F7F4EF] text-sm font-medium hover:bg-[#E8621A] transition-colors">送信する</button>
    </form>

    <!-- Contact Info -->
    <div class="mt-16 pt-12 border-t border-[#DDD9D2] grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-10">
      <div>
        <p class="font-mono-label text-xs mb-4 tracking-widest" style="color:#E8621A">PHONE</p>
        <a href="tel:0120-000-0000" class="font-serif text-2xl text-ink hover:text-[#E8621A] transition-colors">0120-000-0000</a>
        <p class="text-xs text-muted mt-2">営業時間: 9:00-18:00（定休日: 水曜日）</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="font-mono-label text-xs mb-4 tracking-widest" style="color:#E8621A">VISIT</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed mb-2">〒000-0000<br>東京都○○区○○ 1-2-3<br>○○ビル 4F</p>
        <a href="/company.html" class="text-xs text-ink hover:text-[#E8621A] transition-colors border-b border-[#DDD9D2] pb-0.5">地図を見る →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
